Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.54,0:00:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是靈樹森林的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.37,0:00:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有小孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.04,0:00:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個大個男人是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.79,0:00:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們好像變成觀賞物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.42,0:00:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為前排的人醒目啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.96,0:00:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 是妖精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.22,0:00:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然帶著妖精這樣奇怪的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.84,0:00:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是真正的魔女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.18,0:00:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我可不想和你一起相提並論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.47,0:00:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的兩位哪個是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.14,0:00:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 大家 魔女大人在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.35,0:00:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛 鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.82,0:00:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.36,0:00:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.40,0:00:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的小屁孩是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.78,0:00:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩根 這到底在開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.32,0:00:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.78,0:00:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 也難怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.58,0:00:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來一發魔法讓他們開開眼如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.79,0:00:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙就不會不服氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.79,0:00:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.42,0:00:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了引人注目而使用魔法是不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.09,0:00:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我早說了 村長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.88,0:00:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭司大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.92,0:00:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是僧侶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.67,0:00:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情複雜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.43,0:00:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使依靠魔女這種不可靠的迷信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.51,0:01:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也無法解決目前的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.81,0:01:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且摩根 你讓那樣的小丫頭扮成魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.10,0:01:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是打算消除自己一人苟活回來的自責感吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.90,0:01:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣太膚淺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.78,0:01:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.15,0:01:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這副打扮 你們是旅行藝人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.66,0:01:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途中被摩根哀求了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.70,0:01:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你們是來巡演的還是幹什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.29,0:01:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些魔獸可不是你們能對付的來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.25,0:01:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好馬上離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.34,0:01:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是祭司大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.71,0:01:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人仔細看看不是很強壯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.30,0:01:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用趕走也可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.59,0:01:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.34,0:01:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是神明大人給予這個村莊的試煉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.76,0:01:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們唯有祈禱和忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.14,0:01:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧 別管他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.48,0:01:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們好不容易來了 沒進門就被趕走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.56,0:01:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像傻瓜一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.73,0:01:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘即使是演戲或假扮也不要如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.57,0:01:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這裡是聖都 你會被處以火刑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.15,0:02:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女隻是墮落和邪惡的象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.99,0:02:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們帶著病人和小孩長途跋涉已經很疲憊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.83,0:02:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話希望借宿一晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.08,0:02:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 現在這種時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個姑娘在做祈求恢復的巡禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向巡禮者施捨是寺院的規矩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.97,0:02:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是死是活我也不會再管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.72,0:02:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙你的大恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.84,0:02:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 那把劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.05,0:02:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真傢伙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.39,0:02:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個左臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.76,0:02:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村長 請給他們準備房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.89,0:02:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想了妙招呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.31,0:02:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用眼睛好好感受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.07,0:02:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次邂逅對你到底意何在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.33,0:04:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家請把這個綁到手指上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭髮嗎 是你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼把 頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了能使用念話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.84,0:04:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是心靈感應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可疑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.34,0:04:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低能猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰是猴子 你這個傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.64,0:04:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡使用的是施術時持有施術對象一部分的被稱為感染魔術的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.31,0:04:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用指甲頭屋之類的對人下詛咒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.19,0:04:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人只要到某種程度 都可能進行直接的思想交互
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.69,0:04:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這就需要有很咼的氣 靈氣的磁力的連接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.95,0:04:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能相連的只有你嗎 其他人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.87,0:04:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就和沒有修行的人聯擊是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.33,0:04:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此這次和獸鬼的作戰中 希望大家都聽我的指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遒是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼 別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.80,0:05:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰要被你這種小丫頭使喚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.72,0:05:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最合適的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.84,0:05:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把握整個戰況並傳達給大家的只有我這個魔法師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.56,0:05:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實如此 在獸鬼上魔女才是專家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.73,0:05:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣吧 本來她就是對付鬼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.82,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 三等兵向指揮敬禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.45,0:05:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說誰猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想單獨待一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.33,0:05:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.46,0:05:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在練劍嗎 小兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一個人可不安全啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.09,0:05:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大爺你又在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.38,0:05:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想給你們的晚餐準備些魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.89,0:05:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 還有番薯湯再忍耐會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.06,0:05:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來這裡真是個小村莊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.44,0:06:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種山谷裡 能見陽光的時間不到半天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.69,0:06:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爺爺那輩這個村莊是連著街道的 據說很熱鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.45,0:06:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就像你看見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.37,0:06:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這麼說 也不想默默等死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你們很期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小兄弟你為何要和他們一起旅行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那位黑色劍士的侍從嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.76,0:06:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 我在做武者的修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.84,0:06:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯大哥和我有約定要教我劍術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位劍士很強呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟能揮舞那樣巨大的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.90,0:06:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 他強得就和怪物一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.15,0:06:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很崇拜他嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.03,0:06:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崇拜 別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是利用他而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.57,0:06:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為我目前的目標而努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家裡人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事都無所謂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個旁人不會明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.34,0:07:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.21,0:07:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這把年紀還不顧家人去找魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.51,0:07:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有那些村人是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.01,0:07:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對拚命去找魔女的你竟然那麼排斥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.02,0:07:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是群薄情的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.52,0:07:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不如也離開這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.69,0:07:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在這種小地方也沒什麼好的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.03,0:07:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡長眠著我的家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.82,0:07:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被獸鬼殺害的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是更久前死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.99,0:07:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感謝把村子命運寄託給我的村民 因此我冫殳有怨言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.63,0:07:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反而更感謝他們 讓我在死前能再見到那位魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.55,0:07:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人都是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.89,0:07:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小時候也幻想過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說著要去找魔女要去抓妖精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.81,0:08:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後拋下家裡的工作去深山裡森林裡閒逛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.61,0:08:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你說的 我也曾要離開這個小村莊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.90,0:08:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己坐著船從布利達尼斯向海洋出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.53,0:08:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直夢想著這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.12,0:08:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到母親病倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.92,0:08:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時的事已經記不清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.42,0:08:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只知道等察覺到時已經在森林深處迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.63,0:08:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為救母親而去找魔女的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.64,0:08:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彷彿在夢中一樣 我到了那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.60,0:08:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我用帶回家的藥救回了媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她已經很衰老了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.28,0:08:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那以後我就在家做事再也沒去過森林了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回過神時已經這把年紀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.74,0:09:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後時光流逝 記憶也模糊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的曾見過她嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.00,0:09:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但魔女卻在森林深處等著我 和那時一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.59,0:09:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些對就足夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.60,0:09:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我這樣的年輕人不要說那種陳年舊事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的年輕人真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.14,0:09:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那麼普通的一個夢當成年輕時的大事的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.32,0:09:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和正在實現野心的我不要相提並論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的野心會長毛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.66,0:09:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個小鬼對你很依賴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.12,0:09:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼來襲時 村民們能躲藏的就是這個寺院吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.84,0:09:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只能在這布陣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 我必須要振作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 寺院坐落的這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.48,0:10:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.77,0:10:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾出去 魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.94,0:10:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭司大人說了 魔女和獸鬼是一個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.44,0:10:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人火大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.62,0:10:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在勘察陣地嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.58,0:10:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.49,0:10:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那時是不是對那個僧侶有話要說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.33,0:10:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對那個臭僧侶才不想說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是那個僧侶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.59,0:10:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為現在世上的人都錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐落著寺院的這個山丘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.72,0:10:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去曾是祭祀這片土地的精靈的神殿遺蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.80,0:10:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法王廳的寺院大都如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.85,0:10:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踐踏精靈信仰的聖地然後建立起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.31,0:10:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在法王廳的教只是用來誇耀自己權力的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.53,0:11:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們禮讀著神的名字互相爭鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.11,0:11:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禮讀著神的名字尋求救贖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.24,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己想要忘卻的東西說不定反而是救贖自己的關鍵所在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.42,0:11:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡面也有你們魔女嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.09,0:11:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的師傅過去曾在這附近的村落生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奔走於貧困的村莊之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.59,0:11:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向人們傳達精靈的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.14,0:11:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊向他們傳教季節的事一邊治病救人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.31,0:11:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅的魔法救治了很多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.90,0:11:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是隨著法王廳的教團擴展到這一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個村莊開始建起了寺院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直如同翻臉一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們驅趕師傅 把她趕到了森林裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.12,0:11:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那之後師傅就在森林中躲避世人並隱居起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.79,0:11:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而現在竟然好像沒發生過那種事一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能原諒這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.76,0:12:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是師傅吩咐誰要救這個村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.51,0:12:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼不做就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.18,0:12:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是沒有那個意向的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒有必要為了那些討厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以身犯險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個婆婆就要死了不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就更要這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.65,0:12:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人說了就算不喜歡也照做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.57,0:12:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是小孩的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.95,0:12:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個沒禮貌還吊兒郎當的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是不情不願的來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.37,0:12:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個男人不可能是我的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絶對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.84,0:12:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不要亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.00,0:12:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.30,0:12:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給聽不懂話的法露小姐綁頭髮是不是沒有意義啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.68,0:12:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是希凱兒小姐說要綁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.72,0:12:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說念話是靠印象傳導的 我也不太懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.64,0:12:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.14,0:12:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說貫話這次的獸鬼退治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不說起來這次旅行本身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.19,0:13:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都認為應該停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 喀絲卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.62,0:13:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是變樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我辦不到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能看見這個笑容的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該算是值得吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.63,0:13:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風的精靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不被任何東西束縛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能吹到任何地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.39,0:13:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是諷刺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.39,0:13:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是和我最無緣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎廑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼來了 都來寺院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.78,0:13:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是心靈傳送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.20,0:13:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽路畢克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.96,0:13:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.18,0:14:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.64,0:14:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎度回事那個數量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一囗氣吃光我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.97,0:14:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊跑吧這裡也不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.39,0:14:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個吹號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今聒上就來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.69,0:14:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西確實方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.65,0:14:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我們趕緊去寺院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.70,0:14:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽路畢克 想想希凱兒小姐的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.25,0:14:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想明白點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.37,0:14:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.46,0:14:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 想像 想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.05,0:14:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你們了 精靈們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.06,0:14:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.85,0:14:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.61,0:15:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說真的 有這個就能放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法 真正的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.74,0:15:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 就你一個人出風頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.58,0:15:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要出手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.87,0:15:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 火焰喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.25,0:15:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一匹就夠了一匹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.04,0:15:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑啊 要被吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杯水車薪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.47,0:15:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.97,0:15:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙把受傷的伙伴吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.22,0:15:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想變那樣就跑起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.94,0:15:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喀絲卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.07,0:15:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.24,0:15:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個法露小姐會為了別人挺身而出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.70,0:16:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來銀的退魔作用生效了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.12,0:16:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來打開退路 趕緊跑到寺院去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 趕緊進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 有人被包圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些魔女的同行者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了能讓我們逃走用身體擋住獸鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.55,0:16:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣就沒救了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.39,0:16:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太愚蠢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.18,0:16:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.56,0:16:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 那些傢伙不是人能對付的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在 跑到寺院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.55,0:17:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了嗎 祭司大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.22,0:17:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 幹掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.93,0:17:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那個那個人的話就能從獸鬼手上保護村子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 那傢伙好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂哪邊是怪物了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.57,0:17:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確不像一般人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.11,0:17:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是那個人在精神能輕易影響物質的狹間彷徨的結果嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.07,0:17:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.70,0:17:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纏在劍周圍的那個影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎 依巴蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.83,0:17:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妥妥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你說的方位上都貼好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,符咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.38,0:17:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.34,0:17:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我要用魔法在這個寺院張開防壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員趕緊進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個遭報應的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.72,0:17:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村長 趕緊讓那個女孩從房頂下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.43,0:17:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.98,0:17:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔術是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.31,0:17:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我親眼看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.31,0:17:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女孩的同伴隔空砍死獸鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.86,0:17:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個劍士大人的同伴們嗎 那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.07,0:17:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對 腳踏實地腳踏實地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.87,0:18:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤得·海恩 班·海恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.12,0:18:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.62,0:18:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使不得 使不得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.91,0:18:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正忙的呢 不能打擾她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊從這裡下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.50,0:18:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希凱兒是為了誰在做這些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.92,0:18:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 我叫你停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是要住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子正在保護村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不明白嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.14,0:18:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算生命能延續下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.89,0:18:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是靠邪門歪道荀且偷生還有什麼意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.60,0:18:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是天命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.94,0:18:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個男人 和我一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和過去的我一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仗著神的名義 把人逼上死路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有反駁的資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光說你也不懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.84,0:18:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.13,0:18:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誦讀咒文的希凱兒正有神遊天外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.76,0:18:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請把手放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.38,0:19:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打擾我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.06,0:19:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.48,0:19:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被包圍了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.36,0:19:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.24,0:19:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喀絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.78,0:19:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們趕緊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡我一個就夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面的人和女人們拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.87,0:19:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的份也一起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋躲開 過不去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.85,0:19:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 看見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳過我們 不對 飛過去的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.27,0:19:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我們風之軍團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也秀下身手呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊西特羅 這裡暫時交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.41,0:20:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要坦然接受 不能恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喀絲卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.71,0:20:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.67,0:20:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希凱兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.63,0:20:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 神明啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請引導我到您的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.81,0:20:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才就是最後的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.85,0:20:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真實的 一群一群的沒完沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.36,0:20:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希凱兒那小鬼在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.48,0:20:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下不上不行了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的本事說實話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.28,0:20:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 這才是關鍵時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.91,0:20:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 身體被劍帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.54,0:20:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.66,0:20:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.09,0:21:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.42,0:21:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.59,0:21:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 說你們啊 不能只靠小孩子和老頭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.47,0:21:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.43,0:21:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺子  喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.56,0:21:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由虛空中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.64,0:21:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把陸 海 空 火的透明的四人之王召喚至此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.86,0:21:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此陣保吾身周全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.86,0:21:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當溫暖的守護的防禦之火點亮之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.11,0:21:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令所有災禍 不會加之吾身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.96,0:21:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本·蓋普勒 馬魯可圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.17,0:21:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬忒·本 蓋土魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.34,0:21:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本·歐蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.05,0:21:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.74,0:22:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼們 都碎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.53,0:22:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個光輝是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.83,0:22:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷囗在癒合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.70,0:22:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就有救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.96,0:22:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是 那傢伙的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.92,0:18:04.53,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.70,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個神的面前做這種邪惡之事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.57,0:24:05.40,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an7}這也是報應嗎 還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.66,0:24:10.74,Preview,,0,0,0,,我是為了保護他人才挺劍奮起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.16,0:24:14.33,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}正合我意! 你們這些大猴子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.71,0:24:18.79,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}比起百人斬來說不算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.54,0:24:22.50,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}好想再見你一面啊 好久不見
